'''赫敦'''（Hedon）是位於[[英格蘭|英格蘭]][[東約克郡|東約克郡]]的一座小鎮和[[民政教區|民政教區]]，位於胡爾市中心以東{{convert|5|mi|km|0}}。這裡最著名的地標是聖奧古斯特教堂，有「霍德尼斯之王」之稱<ref>{{cite web
 |url         = http://www.dioceseofyork.org.uk/dean20.shtml
 |title       = Deanery of South Holderness
 |accessdate  = 2 August 2007
 |author      = The Diocese of York
 |archiveurl  = https://web.archive.org/web/20070928022733/http://www.dioceseofyork.org.uk/dean20.shtml
 |archivedate = 2007-09-28
 |deadurl     = yes
}}</ref>，被列入英國一級保護建築<ref>{{NHLE|num=1346568|desc=Church of St Augustine|accessdate=12 August 2013}}</ref>。據2011年英國人口普查，赫敦有人口7,100人<ref name="2011 census">{{cite web
 | url = http://www.neighbourhood.statistics.gov.uk/dissemination/LeadKeyFigures.do?a=7&b=11124436&c=hedon&d=16&e=62&g=6381351&i=1001x1003x1032x1004&m=0&r=1&s=1360074052822&enc=1
